  "description": "Engagement-aware automation layer + self-contained timeframe system. v0.7.0 (MINOR): cowork is now self-contained — NEW path convention spice/cowork/daily/YYYY/MM-MMMM/YYYY-MM-DD.md for cowork-owned daily notes; NEW CoworkDailyActions CustomJS class + Daily Note.md Templater template wire the create-flow; cowork-daily-hub-cards retargets from spice/daily → spice/cowork/daily (closes the daily-blueprint cross-reach); CoworkHubNav rewritten from BeaconCards 4-card row → AccentButton centered flex row (matches ScratchDayActions aesthetic), drops 'you are here', OMITS the current-hub button so each hub renders 3 buttons pointing at the other 3; universal nav-pattern (SpaceNavButtons → --- → CoworkHubNav → --- → content) across all 5 hubs + 3 note templates; Weekly/Monthly Note templates compute friendly H1 titles via Templater (Week 20 · May 11–17, 2026 / May 2026); Daily Note H1 (Thursday, May 14, 2026); Timeframes row grows 5 → 6 cards (Daily Hub | Today | Weekly Hub | This Week | Monthly Hub | This Month); NEW cowork-daily rule_fragment. v0.6.0 (MINOR v0.44.0): UX polish + character pass. v0.5.0: nav consolidation. v0.4.0: timeframe scaffolding. v0.3.0: 10 orchestrators + 28 sub-skills.",
