    {
      "type": "notice",
      "message": "cowork@0.7.0 installed. Self-contained pass: cowork now owns its own daily notes at spice/cowork/daily/YYYY/MM-MMMM/YYYY-MM-DD.md (mirrors daily-blueprint shape but inside cowork's own dir). NEW CoworkDailyActions helper renders a '+ Today' button on the Daily Hub. CoworkHubNav rewrites to AccentButton-row aesthetic (matches scratch); drops 'you are here'; OMITS the current-hub button. All 5 cowork hubs + 3 note templates carry the universal nav-pattern (SpaceNavButtons → --- → CoworkHubNav → --- → content). Weekly/Monthly/Daily note templates compute friendly H1 titles via Templater. Timeframes row 5 → 6 cards. Re-render all cowork notes to see the new layout."
